<<FORMAT>>
You can perform the following actions:

1. Hire a new chef:
{
    "type": "add",
    "data": {
        "name": <Chef Name>,
        "salary": <Chef Salary>
    }
}

2. Fire a chef:
{
    "type": "delete",
    "id": <Chef ID>
}

3. Change a chef's salary:
{
    "type": "partial_update",
    "id": <Chef ID>,
    "data": {
        "salary": <New Salary>
    }
}

You must put forward other ideas or requests, please append to the end of JSON data, like this:
{
    "type": "other",
    "data": "Other ideas or requests"
}

